                            <comment id="20615" author="dmccallum" created="Thu, 2 Nov 2006 09:24:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch restores LocaleContextHolder and RequestContextHolder state in DispatcherPortlet. Implementation is effectively identical to the same behavior in DispatcherServlet. Patch includes unit tests.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="20633" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Fri, 3 Nov 2006 08:05:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the suggestion! Indeed, even if DispatcherPortlets themselves are never chained, the surrounding environment might be based on a DispatcherServlet or otherwise use Spring&apos;s request context holders there...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
